```
t!help                      Lists available commands
t!kick [@user] [reason]     Kicks the mentioned user
t!ban [@user] [reason]      Bans the mentioned user
t!mute [@user]              Mutes the mentioned user
t!unmute [@user]            Unmutes the mentioned user
t!deleteChannel [#channel]  Deletes the mentioned channel
t!deleteRole [#channel]     Deletes the mentioned role
t!serververification        Changes the server verification to medium
```
